{"tid":2497318,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞推「BTS聯名套餐」49國名單中不見中國","createTime":"2021-04-20T12:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T13:05:03.000Z","uid":212249,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03efc64656b34bb98baea2eae0137d3bf08fc610","tid":2497318,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣團體BTS（防彈少年團）旋風席捲全球，創下許多K－POP歷史紀錄。昨（19）日他們又再度宣布了一項超狂聯名，全球知名連鎖速食店麥當勞也看上他們「超級帶貨王」的威力，將在全世界49國家推出「BTS聯名套餐」，台灣、港澳都名列其中，卻獨缺中國大陸，迅速引起廣大粉絲討論。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞昨日在官方推特上發布了一張照片，以代表團員7人的7根薯條拼出BTS的團體Logo，正式宣布將在5月推出「BTS聯名套餐」。從發行國家圖表中能看到，從5月26日開始最先能吃到的是美國、澳洲、巴西以及加拿大等國家，5月27日南韓、新加坡也隨即上市，台灣則是要等到6月9日才吃的到。<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報導，「BTS聯名套餐」的內容將會以成員愛吃的菜單，像是麥克雞塊、薯條配上特殊的甜辣醬與美式海鮮醬（Cajun Sauce）加上飲料；另外BTS成員們也會獨家獻聲，為麥當勞演唱招牌音效，超強合作消息一出，也讓A.R.M.Y（BTS粉絲團）們大呼期待：「這真的太扯了」、「不是粉絲都會想嘗試」、「薯條不會只有7根吧（笑）」、「看我還不吃爆」。<br />\n<br />\n但名單中有香港、澳門，卻沒有中國大陸的門市，也讓微博上網友失望留言：「哭了，怎麼會沒有大陸」、「金拱門（指麥當勞）別不知好歹」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-newtalk-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/s.newtalk.tw/album/news/566/607e427fc0e35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-newtalk-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F566%2F607e427fc0e35.jpg&h=e034ebce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bf70e7dcb1970f936eb8e226764f6a94cbc5ae7","tid":2497318,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-20/565920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-04-20%2F565920&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ0qdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=a80d9731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-20/565920</a>"},{"pid":"5df6da9675dcc63feaddd8b884da33cfab91e19e","tid":2497318,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"全球BTS餐<br />\n香港姜B餐<br />\n姜B = 香港BTS 已認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c519fe577997e534d2bd5f93f50fa8a8e9a8862","tid":2497318,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有香港同台灣"},{"pid":"608b41593ee5184a29aa9d288816c5a53dc95493","tid":2497318,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c519fe577997e534d2bd5f93f50fa8a8e9a8862","tid":2497318,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有香港同台灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:23:51.000Z","msg":"澳門都有"},{"pid":"eea90e3db0d271a938aedd3f46a9e652ab107d3e","tid":2497318,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c519fe577997e534d2bd5f93f50fa8a8e9a8862","tid":2497318,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有香港同台灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"香港麥當勞深黃 唔反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8425acbceb55e87ecdd0573af319ce6c843c99","tid":2497318,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"中國人不吃這一套餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f72e55337e411fd578efe66a75272f0aab6f3e","tid":2497318,"uid":18244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8425acbceb55e87ecdd0573af319ce6c843c99","tid":2497318,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"中國人不吃這一套餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}